text: Karagayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Imendyashevsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 297 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Krasnousolsky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Karagayevo
